===Etymology===

Fr. Greek ''sphairos'' ball.

===Noun===

#A three-dimensional object that is perfectly round from all directions.
#(''Mathematics'') The set:<math> \{x \in R^3|\,\, |x|=r \}; r \in R^+</math>
#The area influenced by a country (''sphere of influence'')

